race.comment: GALACTIC STAR (3) was well found on debut and didn't let supporters down with a solid win over this track and trip. Winning hoop Thompson retains the ride and looks well-placed to feature in the finish again. DR FARTHING (5) looked handy saluting at Toowoomba when facing the starter for the first time and will have come on with that win now in the locker. Genuine top-three commodity. MAKING NEWS (7) gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination and shouldn't be discounted lightly. In the mix. The consistent LOVECATS (8) has hit the top-five in all five starts to date and is a must for the multiples from the inside alley.
